com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.server

Class HostPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.server.HostPage

  • public class HostPage
extends java.lang.Object
    Generates a GWT host page based on the parameters passed to the constructor and initializer methods of the inner class HostPage.Builder and the state of the Site, Style, Page and Landing objects in the GAE Data-store. The resulting HTML page includes a reference to a GWT <module>.nocache.js in a <script> HTML tag. This page may also contain HTML elements in its body, some of which your GWT module may reference or modify.
